        "Description": "Good morning 47,  amidst the chaos of the noisy markets and the on going coup in morrocco some less than desirable Zaydan loyalists have began to spread the word and make propaganda of the yet to be dictator. While our client would prefer to stay away from the conflict as much as possible in every single way, it would still be convenient for them to have these loud speakers taken care of.\r\rTo shift suspicion away from this being a hit, the client has asked us to make the murders look like the handywork of a vigilante amidst the consulate&#39;s security staff. This means you&#39;ll have to resort to the same type of gear, so that might be a problem 47.\r\rSeems easy enough, you might even enjoy this one 47, acting as somebone you aren&#39;t is your specialty anyway.\r\rGood luck 47, I&#39;ll leave you to prepare.\r\n\r\nExit: Garage Car\r\n<HCCE>",
